She's a poor thing, and she's pretty.

501
00:32:29,739 --> 00:32:32,951
But at the very least,

502
00:32:33,451 --> 00:32:36,454
she shouldn't have a son, should she?

503
00:32:37,205 --> 00:32:40,416
Am I asking for too much right now?

504
00:32:42,168 --> 00:32:46,339
Mom, think of this
as buy one get one free.

505
00:32:46,631 --> 00:32:49,342
You can get a daughter-in-law
and a grandson at once.

506
00:32:50,051 --> 00:32:52,804
Goodness. Why did you have to be
crushing garlic right now?

507
00:32:54,097 --> 00:32:57,308
I'm not going to blame her.

508
00:32:58,017 --> 00:33:00,812
I don't want to go over to Camellia
to say something to her.

509
00:33:01,312 --> 00:33:02,605
I understand that

510
00:33:02,689 --> 00:33:05,525
Dongbaek has no feelings for you,
but you're obsessed with her.

511
00:33:05,608 --> 00:33:08,194
I'm just going to focus on you.

512
00:33:08,403 --> 00:33:12,031
So you and I have to come to a decision.

513
00:33:12,657 --> 00:33:13,700
Make your choice!

514
00:33:14,575 --> 00:33:17,120
I mean... Well, I...

515
00:33:19,831 --> 00:33:22,709
I can't choose one as if I'm
choosing what food I like.

516
00:33:23,251 --> 00:33:24,210
BAEKDU MARINATED CRAB

517
00:33:24,293 --> 00:33:26,421
Okay, fine. Half-and-half.

518
00:33:27,213 --> 00:33:29,757
Don't be ridiculous. That's not an option.

519
00:33:29,841 --> 00:33:32,301
I like her so much. What can I do?

520
00:33:32,927 --> 00:33:36,597
I want to see her as soon as I wake up.

521
00:33:36,681 --> 00:33:39,517
I want to run over
to see her right now, too.

522
00:33:41,644 --> 00:33:45,064
My feet are the magnetic north pole,
and Camellia is the south pole.

523
00:33:46,149 --> 00:33:48,317
Does that analogy make some sense?

524
00:33:48,401 --> 00:33:49,902
What a load of bullshit.

525
00:33:50,028 --> 00:33:51,863
Do I need to kick some sense into you?

526
00:33:52,739 --> 00:33:56,367
I can't stop my feelings for her
and my feet taking me there.

527
00:33:57,493 --> 00:34:01,831
Then you can stop seeing her
for just two months.

528
00:34:01,914 --> 00:34:04,250
If you still feel the same after that,

529
00:34:04,751 --> 00:34:07,253
I will extenuate your actions.

530
00:34:09,756 --> 00:34:12,383
Do you think my love will only last
for a couple of months?

531
00:34:13,301 --> 00:34:14,844
It'll last forever!

532
00:34:21,768 --> 00:34:22,977
Should we get started?

533
00:34:23,186 --> 00:34:26,230
No, I want the director.

534
00:34:28,191 --> 00:34:29,192
Ma'am.

535
00:34:29,859 --> 00:34:33,237
You have to make an appointment
two weeks ahead to see her.

536
00:34:33,821 --> 00:34:35,573
Our chief is really good, too.

537
00:34:35,656 --> 00:34:38,409
She worked in the Hongdae area
for three years.

538
00:34:38,910 --> 00:34:41,746
I'm sure you're great.

539
00:34:42,497 --> 00:34:44,332
But I'm going to go meet

540
00:34:45,291 --> 00:34:47,543
the woman my husband's been seeing
after doing my hair.

541
00:34:48,753 --> 00:34:49,837
Goodness.

542
00:34:50,296 --> 00:34:53,007
Director. Director?

543
00:34:58,971 --> 00:35:00,598
Rod number three.

544
00:35:01,015 --> 00:35:01,933
No.

545
00:35:02,683 --> 00:35:05,520
Everyone has a limit
that they must defend.

546
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:08,439
My limit is my pride.

547
00:35:08,523 --> 00:35:09,899
I'll use the best products.

548
00:35:09,982 --> 00:35:12,193
I don't want to care
about someone like Dongbaek.

549
00:35:12,485 --> 00:35:15,947
I wanted to ignore her
with all that I have.

550
00:35:22,203 --> 00:35:26,207
What brings you here?
I thought you never stop by the building.

551
00:35:28,543 --> 00:35:32,296
CAMELLIA

552
