so start investigating with this.

706
00:46:08,974 --> 00:46:11,268
I'm sure Joker is somewhere in here.

707
00:46:20,194 --> 00:46:22,571
I met her at church.

708
00:46:23,530 --> 00:46:25,032
-I mean...
-Today's reading.

709
00:46:26,283 --> 00:46:28,035
"When you're waiting for tomorrow..."

710
00:46:28,619 --> 00:46:30,496
Will the practice end in two hours?

711
00:46:30,579 --> 00:46:32,790
I need to go pick up Pil-gu later.

712
