JUNE 29, 2014

713
00:46:33,999 --> 00:46:36,001
You should learn
during the weekdays as well.

714
00:46:36,502 --> 00:46:38,045
Get a certificate in skincare.

715
00:46:38,128 --> 00:46:40,422
Then change the signboard
to "Camellia Aesthetics."

716
00:46:40,506 --> 00:46:42,758
You'll become a person
with a professional career.

717
00:46:43,467 --> 00:46:45,469
I'm a professional
at making stir-fried pork.

718
00:46:45,552 --> 00:46:51,016
OK AESTHETIC

719
00:46:54,394 --> 00:46:56,396
Are you sure
you're doing practical training?

720
00:46:56,730 --> 00:46:58,232
Am I being used as a guinea pig?

721
00:46:58,607 --> 00:47:01,652
I know it's second-hand,
but it cost me a million won. Don't worry.

722
00:47:02,402 --> 00:47:05,113
I feel like you're using me
to test the second-hand machine.

723
00:47:11,036 --> 00:47:11,995
Is this okay?

724
00:47:15,499 --> 00:47:16,500
Just a second.

725
00:47:17,251 --> 00:47:19,336
-Hello?
-The door looks weird.

726
00:47:19,670 --> 00:47:20,712
A reservation?

727
00:47:21,672 --> 00:47:24,675
Can you come right away?
